text: Keith Caple was a weightlifter from Australia. Keith competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics. He was born on 6 May 1923 and died on 29 November 2006.Keith Caple == References == Category:1923 births Category:2006 deaths Category:Australian weightlifters Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Sportspeople from Sydney
